{"id": 972, "genre": 1001, "title": "发生什么小事让你觉得一天都被毁掉了？", "description": "那能怎么办！我可是娇嫩的现代人。（题图来自：John Holcroft）", "record_count": 6234, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160702183719P7CurocfVGAiHJsp.JPG", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-04-30T01:00:49Z", "options": [{"id": 71936, "content": "刚一起床，就看到微信里老板发来的几个重要指示。", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 362351}, {"id": 72192, "content": "有他玛撸了?", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 591149}, {"id": 72960, "content": "收银台前没带钱。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 592326}, {"id": 71937, "content": "没有WiFi", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 566091}, {"id": 72193, "content": "又他玛撸了?", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 591149}, {"id": 71938, "content": "TA不理我了。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 127182}, {"id": 72194, "content": "好不容易哄睡的娃被人吵醒?", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 591153}, {"id": 72450, "content": "突然来个电话，说找你有事", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 591521}, {"id": 71939, "content": "吃早餐时，油弄到衣服上。", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 556885}, {"id": 72195, "content": "大清早被导师的电话打醒匆匆忙忙赶去办公室却被放了一天的鸽子", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 591152}, {"id": 71940, "content": "收到一个贱人的邮件，问你“Much appreciate if you can list/outline priorities or \"work in progress\" with each ” 你能要点脸么？你以为你是谁？", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 590563}, {"id": 72196, "content": "早上快迟到的时候醒来，并且知道自己还要上课的时候", "image": "img/option/option/20160607192702yQ27s39bDSnGZ06E", "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 591150}, {"id": 72964, "content": "准备看电影时朋友走散了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 517933}, {"id": 71941, "content": "闹钟七点，六点小腹坠胀?", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 589192}, {"id": 72197, "content": "放假过后 期中考试???", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 591154}, {"id": 73221, "content": "早上跟别人吵架", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 592970}, {"id": 73477, "content": "北京早高峰::>_<::", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 423285}, {"id": 72198, "content": "支持的球队输球了", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 545053}, {"id": 71943, "content": "考完理综", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 548131}, {"id": 72199, "content": "大姨妈来了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 591158}, {"id": 72455, "content": "完美的51被老妈拍黄瓜声吵醒！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 591543}, {"id": 74247, "content": "被插队\r\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 593834}, {"id": 81927, "content": "没有见到想见的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 622537}, {"id": 71944, "content": "一起床看到堆积如山的作业", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 341831}, {"id": 72200, "content": "没有Wi-Fi或者没有?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 552264}, {"id": 73224, "content": "等快递", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 164345}, {"id": 71689, "content": "遇到不认路的uber司机", "image": null, "praise_count": 112, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 327855}, {"id": 71945, "content": "没有睡好！", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 426807}, {"id": 72201, "content": "没睡醒", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 591167}, {"id": 72457, "content": "开开心心换好衣服出门发现下雨了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 591564}, {"id": 71690, "content": "闹钟⏰", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 365039}, {"id": 71946, "content": "没有人对我说早上好", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 590580}, {"id": 72202, "content": "一件甚至不重要的事没处理好", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 591166}, {"id": 73482, "content": "出门忘带眼镜", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 580150}, {"id": 71691, "content": "说好的快递 并没有来……", "image": null, "praise_count": 587, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 490384}, {"id": 71947, "content": "朋友给我带到距离我家差不多二十公里的地方，把我扔下跑了", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 578409}, {"id": 72203, "content": "本以为今天工作很轻松，结果一到办公室忙成狗。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 475326}, {"id": 72459, "content": "焦灼", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 567885}, {"id": 71692, "content": "早上第一节有课。大二每早几乎都在挣扎。", "image": null, "praise_count": 81, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 411017}, {"id": 71948, "content": "贱人开口", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 590563}, {"id": 72204, "content": "滴滴也打不到车", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 394195}, {"id": 72460, "content": "天，还没写论文；天，还要写论文", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 201975}, {"id": 73484, "content": "被通知舍友的狗尿在我的床上", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 593641}, {"id": 71693, "content": "说好的快递 并没有送来……", "image": null, "praise_count": 36, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 490384}, {"id": 71949, "content": "第一次认真做的作业真的被?叼走了", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 590586}, {"id": 72205, "content": "早起賴床部落戰爭連輸三場 感覺世界背棄了偶", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 525367}, {"id": 73997, "content": "明明说好的可以赖床了，结果要升国旗…", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 595145}, {"id": 71694, "content": "早起毁一天", "image": null, "praise_count": 404, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 542160}, {"id": 71950, "content": "今天竟然要上班！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 571768}, {"id": 72206, "content": "明天不用上班熬夜了晚睡结果转天却比上班起的还早", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 482523}]}